{"tid":2274141,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"無懼爭議！華為Mate40Pro繼續混用Samsung、京東方、LG螢幕，「唔聞mon」都分得出","createTime":"2020-11-06T08:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T12:54:20.000Z","uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"79055150c4f3131dfc055058d262c29bcf69a505","tid":2274141,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:41:55.000Z","msg":"只有最貴嘅Mate 40 RS保時捷係用Samsung OLED，其他型號請抽獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下轉自知乎：<br />\n<br />\n周冬雨和鑽石的差距，如下圖，亮度同樣拉到最高。<br />\n一眼看上去沒區別的情況是因為沒有對比，有了對比就非常明顯了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2hMkEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2hMkEQ.jpg&h=1dcf81eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bNuu2Tb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbNuu2Tb.jpg&h=9d8c8fab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95ijFER.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95ijFER.jpg&h=5d4a0c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周冬雨的最大問題不只是像素密度，這個很多人都沒搞清楚重點，周冬雨的毛病在於螢幕「從色準、色域、通透度、可視角度」全方位的劣勢，像素密度只是其中一個副作用。<br />\n<br />\n而且更重要的是，如果旁邊真的恰好有同型號的不同屏幕供應商設備對比，真的能一眼看出來。不要把普通人當成睿智，他們不懂參數，但是他們不瞎。"},{"pid":"a47895534f9cba1a7204b805c744f74145c39342","tid":2274141,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T08:42:36.000Z","msg":"前情提要<br />\n<br />\n華為P40Pro混用京東方、LG OLED螢幕再惹爭議，華為粉絲帶顯微鏡買手機：我要買到LG螢幕的手機！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2021801\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2021801</a>"},{"pid":"670139b92d15c0d3e657cb4dbaf8eb390cfa7cef","tid":2274141,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T09:02:54.000Z","msg":"又學埋蘋果啲衰野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb9f5c127675acb990c4de71c55e811ae820975","tid":2274141,"uid":158977,"like":5,"disl